column16: Justin Upton singles on a line drive to center fielder Adam Eaton.   Miguel Cabrera scores.    J.  D.   Martinez to 2nd.
Tyler Danish intentionally walks J.   Martinez.

White Sox challenged (tag play), call on the field was overturned: Nick Castellanos singles on a line drive to center fielder Adam Eaton.  Miguel Cabrera to 3rd.    Nick Castellanos out at 2nd, center fielder Adam Eaton to shortstop Tim Anderson.
Alcides Escobar flies out to center fielder Adam Eaton.

Whit Merrifield singles on a ground ball to left fielder J.  B.   Shuck.  Cheslor Cuthbert out at home on the throw, left fielder J.   Shuck to catcher Alex Avila.   Jarrod Dyson to 3rd.    Whit Merrifield to 2nd on the throw.
Christian Colon lines out to right fielder Avisail Garcia.
Cheslor Cuthbert singles on a ground ball to right fielder Avisail Garcia.   Salvador Perez to 3rd.    Paulo Orlando to 2nd.
Paulo Orlando singles on a soft line drive to center fielder Adam Eaton.   Reymond Fuentes scores.    Salvador Perez to 2nd.
Salvador Perez singles on a sharp ground ball to left fielder Melky Cabrera.   Reymond Fuentes to 2nd.
Lorenzo Cain grounds out, shortstop Tim Anderson to first baseman Jose Abreu.
